  • Classes in org.cloudbus.cloudsim.schedulers used by org.cloudbus.cloudsim 
    Class and Description
    CloudletScheduler
    An interface to be implemented by each class that provides a policy of scheduling performed by a virtual machine to run its Cloudlets.

    An interface to be implemented by VmScheduler objects in order to provide scheduling algorithms that allocate host's PEs for VMs running on it.

  • Classes in org.cloudbus.cloudsim.schedulers used by org.cloudbus.cloudsim.schedulers 
    Class and Description
    CloudletScheduler
    An interface to be implemented by each class that provides a policy of scheduling performed by a virtual machine to run its Cloudlets.
    CloudletSchedulerAbstract
    Implements the basic features of a CloudletScheduler, representing the policy of scheduling performed by a virtual machine to run its Cloudlets.
    CloudletSchedulerTimeShared
    CloudletSchedulerTimeShared implements a policy of scheduling performed by a virtual machine to run its Cloudlets.
    VmScheduler
    An interface to be implemented by VmScheduler objects in order to provide scheduling algorithms that allocate host's PEs for VMs running on it.
    VmSchedulerAbstract
    VmSchedulerAbstract is an abstract class that represents the policy used by a Virtual Machine Monitor (VMM) to share processing power of a PM among VMs running in a host.
    VmSchedulerTimeShared
    VmSchedulerTimeShared is a Virtual Machine Monitor (VMM) allocation policy that allocates one or more PEs from a PM to a VM, and allows sharing of PEs by multiple VMs.
